name: Wifimask
tagline: Software to help you get onto the school's wifi
body:
### Welcome to WifiMask software.
This software will help you connect to wifi networks that use wireless whitelisting.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with WifiMask? Talk to Jasper Holton in person or email jasper@holton.io
